<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Warning Letter</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #1f2937;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 48px 40px;
            background: white;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .letterhead {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: flex-start;
            padding-bottom: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 36px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }

        .company-name {
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #111827;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        }

        .company-address {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #4b5563;
            line-height: 1.6;
            max-width: 280px;
        }

        .doc-badge {
            text-align: right;
        }

        .doc-title {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #fecaca;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.06em;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .doc-date {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #6b7280;
        }

        .doc-date strong {
            color: #111827;
        }

        .confidential-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 9999px;
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
            background: #fef2f2;
            color: #dc2626;
            margin-top: 8px;
        }

        .section-label {
            font-size: 11px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.06em;
            color: #6b7280;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .recipient {
            margin-bottom: 32px;
        }

        .recipient-name {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #111827;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .recipient-detail {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #4b5563;
        }

        .subject {
            background: #fef2f2;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 16px 20px;
            border-left: 4px solid #ef4444;
            margin-bottom: 28px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #991b1b;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .content {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #374151;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        .content p {
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .incident-box {
            background: #f9fafb;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 24px;
            margin: 24px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #6b7280;
        }

        .incident-title {
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #111827;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.04em;
        }

        .incident-text {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #374151;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        .action-section {
            background: #fffbeb;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 24px;
            margin: 24px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b;
        }

        .action-title {
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #92400e;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.04em;
        }

        .action-list {
            padding-left: 20px;
        }

        .action-list li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #78350f;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .closing {
            margin-top: 24px;
        }

        .signature-section {
            margin-top: 48px;
        }

        .sig-label {
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #6b7280;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.04em;
            margin-bottom: 48px;
        }

        .sig-line {
            border-top: 1px solid #d1d5db;
            padding-top: 8px;
            width: 250px;
        }

        .sig-name {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #111827;
        }

        .sig-role {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #6b7280;
        }

        .ack-section {
            margin-top: 48px;
            background: #f9fafb;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 24px;
        }

        .ack-title {
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #111827;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.04em;
        }

        .ack-fields {
            display: flex;
            gap: 40px;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #6b7280;
        }

        .ack-field {
            flex: 1;
        }

        .ack-line {
            border-bottom: 1px solid #d1d5db;
            margin-top: 32px;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 48px;
            text-align: center;
            padding-top: 24px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            color: #9ca3af;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="letterhead">
        <div>
            <div class="company-name">{{companyName}}</div>
            <div class="company-address">{{{companyAddress}}}</div>
        </div>
        <div class="doc-badge">
            <div class="doc-title">WARNING</div>
            <div class="doc-date"><strong>Date:</strong> {{issueDate}}</div>
            <div class="confidential-badge">Confidential</div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="recipient">
        <div class="section-label">To</div>
        <div class="recipient-name">{{employeeName}}</div>
        <div class="recipient-detail">{{position}}, {{department}}</div>
    </div>

    <div class="subject">Subject: Warning — {{violationType}}</div>

    <div class="content">
        <p>Dear {{#if employeeName}}{{employeeName}}{{else}}Employee{{/if}},</p>

        <p>This letter is being issued to bring to your attention a serious concern regarding your conduct/performance
            at {{companyName}}.</p>

        <div class="incident-box">
            <div class="incident-title">Incident Details</div>
            <div class="incident-text">{{{incidentDescription}}}</div>
        </div>

        <p>This behavior is in violation of company policies and is not acceptable. As per our company guidelines, such
            actions can have serious consequences including but not limited to suspension or termination of employment.
        </p>

        <div class="action-section">
            <div class="action-title">Expected Corrective Actions</div>
            <ul class="action-list">
                <li>Immediate improvement in the area of concern is expected.</li>
                <li>You must adhere to all company policies and guidelines going forward.</li>
                <li>Any repeat occurrence will lead to further disciplinary action.</li>
                <li>You are expected to maintain cordial relations with colleagues and superiors.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <p>We hope that you will take this warning seriously and make the necessary improvements. The management is
            willing to support you in making these improvements, but continued violations will not be tolerated.</p>

        <p>This letter will be placed in your personnel file for record.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="signature-section">
        <div class="sig-label">Issued By</div>
        <div class="sig-line">
            <div class="sig-name">{{#if hrContactPerson}}{{hrContactPerson}}{{else}}HR Manager{{/if}}</div>
            <div class="sig-role">{{#if managerTitle}}{{managerTitle}}{{else}}Head, HR Department{{/if}}</div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="ack-section">
        <div class="ack-title">Employee Acknowledgment</div>
        <p style="font-size: 13px; color: #4b5563; margin-bottom: 16px;">I acknowledge receipt of this warning letter
            and understand its contents.</p>
        <div class="ack-fields">
            <div class="ack-field">
                <div>Employee Signature</div>
                <div class="ack-line"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="ack-field">
                <div>Date</div>
                <div class="ack-line"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>This is a confidential HR document. {{companyName}}</p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>